 collection where multiple employees might share the exact same salary.
Task: Write a MongoDB query (or aggregation pipeline) to find the $2^\text{nd}$ 
highest salary from this collection. Your solution must correctly handle cases where 
the highest salary is duplicated (e.g., if salaries are [100, 100, 90, 80], the $2^\text{nd}$
 highest salary should be 90).

 db.employees.insertMany([
  { name: "Alice", salary: 100000, department: "Engineering" },
